ist Party]]\n| style=\"background:{{Democratic Unionist Party/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Peter Robinson (Northern Ireland politician)|Peter Robinson]]</small>\n| 8\n| 1.2%\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|8|650|hex={{Democratic Unionist Party/meta/color}}}}\n| 168,216\n| 0.6%\n| {{percentage bar|0.6||c={{Democratic Unionist Party/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Scottish National Party]]\n| style=\"background:{{Scottish National Party/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Alex Salmond]]</small>\n| 6\n| 0.9%\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|6|650|hex={{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}}}\n| 491,386\n| 1.7%\n| {{percentage bar|1.7||c={{Scottish National Party/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Sinn F\u00e9in]]\n| style=\"background:{{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Gerry Adams]]</small>\n| 5\n| 0.8%\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|5|650|hex={{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}}}}\n| 171,942\n| 0.6%\n| {{percentage bar|0.6||c={{Sinn F\u00e9in/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Plaid Cymru]]\n| style=\"background:{{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}}\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Ieuan Wyn Jones]]</small>\n| 3\n| 0.5%\n| data-sort-value=\"\" | {{Infobox political party/seats|3|650|hex={{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}}}}\n| 165,394\n| 0.6%\n| {{percentage bar|0.6||c={{Plaid Cymru/meta/color}}|border-color=#c0c0c0|background-color=#f0f0f0}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Social Democratic & Labour Party]]\n| style=\"background:{{Social Democratic and Labour Party/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | <small>[[Margaret Ritchie (politician)|Margaret Ritchie]]</small>\n| 3\n| 0.5%\n| data-sort-value=\"\" |